replies.body:
its so that once you start building armor lategame rather than earlygame you can more effectively spend your defense gold.

If you buy it early it will just get penetrated, if you get hp instead then all they'll have to shred that is some % hp items and abilities with kindof gated usage. HP items also give you more damage usually or help you deal it. {{item:3751}} {{item:3071}} {{item:3742}} {{item:3401}} {{item:3800}} {{item:3053}} {{item:3748}} 

could be wrong I guess but armor is more of an afterthought in my opinion until lategame unless you have immediate need because someone is really strong or because you need a particular ability on a particular champ regardless of how good the armor actually is as long as it is cost effective.
